<title>Pi̱ki ʋba binili, Ushi Chisʋs ƲIT1008</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki ʋba binili, Ushi Chisʋs,
 Shilombish Holitopa pin Chihowa,
 Aiokcha̱ya ya̱ pim atahli hoka,
 Aiokpahanchit hʋsh taloho̱washke.</lyrics>
<aka>Doxology</aka>
